OL,3,CFailed attempt to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Con former Lincoln airbase has cost #48m
OL,6,FHome Office accounts have revealed
OL,7,F#48m was wasted on a plan to house
OL,8,Fasylum seekers on a former Lincoln
OL,9,Fairbase.
OL,11,FIn March 2023, it was announced RAF
OL,12,FScampton was to house 2,000 migrants
OL,13,Fas part of proposals by the previous
OL,14,FConservative government to reduce the
OL,15,Freliance on hotels.
OL,17,FThe scheme was met with widespread
OL,18,Fanger and disbelief in the local area.
