OL,3,CFailed attempt to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Con former Lincoln airbase has cost #48m
OL,6,FPlans were scrapped in September as
OL,7,Fpart of an election pledge by the new
OL,8,FLabour administration.
OL,10,FNobody was ever housed at the site `
OL,11,Fthe former home of the Dambusters `
OL,12,Fdespite millions being poured into the
OL,13,Fproject.
OL,15,FThe level of losses have recently been
OL,16,Fpublished in the Home Office's
OL,17,Faccounts for the last year. It also
OL,18,Fshowed costs could have ballooned as
OL,19,Fhigh as #180m if the project had been
OL,20,Fpursued for another three years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
