OL,3,CFailed attempt to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Con former Lincoln airbase has cost #48m
OL,6,FThe government has previously admitted
OL,7,Fthat a total of around #60m was spent
OL,8,Fon the site, of which #48.5m has been
OL,9,Frecorded as a loss.
OL,11,FLincoln MP Hamish Falconer told ITV
OL,12,FNews: "I'm honestly furious. I've been
OL,13,Fopposed to this plan since the very
OL,14,Fbeginning. We always said this wasn't
OL,15,Fgoing to work for lots of obvious
OL,16,Freasons.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
