OL,3,CFailed attempt to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Con former Lincoln airbase has cost #48m
OL,6,F"I saw the site, just about a month
OL,7,Fago, and I could not believe - with
OL,8,Ffury - all the NHS spending that has
OL,9,Fgone on in Scampton for a plan that
OL,10,Fwas never going to work. That money
OL,11,Fshould have gone on Lincoln County
OL,12,FHospital.
OL,14,F"What we want to see is the site used
OL,15,Ffor proper commercial purposes. It
OL,16,Fshould be bringing in jobs. It should
OL,17,Fbe reflecting the heritage of RAF
OL,18,FScampton.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
