OL,4,Con former Lincoln airbase has cost #48m
OL,6,F"Obviously, there is an issue in
OL,7,Frelation to asylum seekers that needs
OL,8,Fto be dealt with, but RAF Scampton
OL,9,Fshould be for different purposes and
OL,10,Fthat's what I've always said."
OL,12,FSarah Carter, from Save Our Scampton,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We're nearly a year down the
OL,14,Fline and we're still none the wiser
OL,15,Fwhat's going to happen here.
