OL,6,F"All that money wasted, and they're
OL,7,Fstill wasting it. It's just
OL,8,Fhaemorrhaging money, and we want an
OL,9,Fend to this so we can stop spending
OL,10,Fthe money and so we know what's going
OL,11,Fto be happening."
OL,13,FBacked by West Lindsey District
OL,14,FCouncil, Scampton Holdings wants to
OL,15,Fdevelop the site. They're keen to push
OL,16,Fahead with its regeneration plans to
OL,17,Fcreate a hub for heritage, aviation,
OL,18,Fdefence and space.
