OL,6,FIn a report shared with ITV News - the
OL,7,Fcompany said the project would bring
OL,8,Fin #5m every year to the local visitor
OL,9,Feconomy, support more than 750 jobs,
OL,10,Fand generate an estimated #25m.
OL,12,FSally Grindrod-Smith is heavily
OL,13,Finvolved in the West Lindsey District
OL,14,FCouncil's plans for the regeneration
OL,15,Fwith Scampton Holdings. She said: "I
OL,16,Fhear on a daily basis how frustrated
OL,17,Fthe community are. You can see the
OL,18,Fsite is deteriorating rapidly and
OL,19,Fthere's real concerns over whether
OL,20,Fwe'll be able to bring this back into
OL,21,Fuse.
