OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "A
OL,7,Freview carried out in September 2024
OL,8,Fdetermined that, due to decisions
OL,9,Ftaken by the previous government, the
OL,10,Fcosts associated with the Scampton
OL,11,Fsite had surged well beyond initial
OL,12,Festimates and no longer delivered
OL,13,Fvalue for money for taxpayers.
OL,15,F"The cost of exiting this site was
OL,16,Fminimal compared to the projected
OL,17,Fminimum #180 million required to keep
OL,18,Fit running until March 2027."
